org.labrad.qubits.util
Class ComplexArray

java.lang.Object
  org.labrad.qubits.util.ComplexArray

public class ComplexArray
extends Object

A utility class that encapsulates an array of complex numbers. This class is much more efficient than having an array of Complex objects because only two arrays need to be allocated, not one object per element in the array. In addition, this class has convenience methods for converting to and from LabRAD data.
